For installing c version of iClass (linux):

git clone https://github.com/Dowin452/iClass
cd iClass
gcc iclass.c -o iclass -lncurses
sudo mv iclass /usr/local/bin/

and you can run it by : iclass


++++


For installing Python version of iClass (linux):

1 : install the python package in your distro
2 : install git
3 : pip install curses (if you don't have it)
4 : git clone https://github.com/Dowin452/iClass
5 : cd iClass
6 : chmod +x iclass.py
7 : ./iclass
